      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OSPREY CHRONOS (2) hit the ground running off the low draw last start and was never headed (16.91) at this track in a Grade 6 over 300m. Can make it two on the bounce. FLYING HUGO (5) charged out of the boxes with a strong early split and went straight to the front, scoring an all the way win (16.94) over 300m at this track. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. LOVE SHINE (1) is yet to miss the frame this course and distance. Is drawn well on the inside. Last start finished 2nd in a Grade 6 on February 25 over 300m at this track behind OSPREY CHRONOS beaten 4.5 lengths (17.20). Rates a key chance on best figures. CURRENCY LAD (7) did a good job to finish second last time out over 300m at this track (17.35) in a Grade 6, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
